{"tid":147622,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求指點 - 台灣金門, 去3日夠唔夠","createTime":"2017-03-08T03:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T14:23:26.000Z","uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aebe80c804bf23786398f6c2938be43877f5d1c","tid":147622,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"原先諗住去4日, 但驚1個人會悶.<br />\n<br />\n問1. 想問去3日夠唔夠<br />\n問2. 香港出發搭高鐵去廈門再過金門 要幾多個鐘?<br />\n問3. 有咩係必去, 必食<br />\n問4. 唔識渣車,唔識踏單車, 島上交通點算?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a28c78c2e67bb25c4769e4218c6a8e7ec0e483","tid":147622,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d319c3cdf6bd3f7a6b73ed029968fde30f9e50","tid":147622,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998ea9f78fec099bb098c7c1fb405a5d5e64fb79","tid":147622,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"搭台灣好行巴士<br />\n一共四條線<br />\n分兩日搭<br />\n等於兜晒成個金門行晒主要景點<br />\n<br />\n當然仲要留返一日爬山啦"},{"pid":"b6900a2e4889b1aeec6f9da9ccfcd90df4efbec8","tid":147622,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭台灣好行巴士<br />\n一共四條線<br />\n分兩日搭<br />\n等於兜晒成個金門行晒主要景點<br />\n<br />\n當然仲要留返一日爬山啦</blockquote><br />\n爬咩山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec36b47008a0dfa995391cef203970af3333aa3b","tid":147622,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"太武山<br />\n<br />\n睇蔣中正題果幾個大字（毋忘在莒）"},{"pid":"9f83c4cb979deb9d95f715fcdf27aaefbee7e4c2","tid":147622,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太武山<br />\n<br />\n睇蔣中正題果幾個大字（毋忘在莒）</blockquote><br />\nTHANKS BRO<br />\n仲有咩地方一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582dee1e9bab45d51c4b231a572cb5419393254f","tid":147622,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"其實搭台灣好行已經差不多cover曬所有景點<br />\n仲有免費講解＋完全無購物點<br />\n但如果你鍾意戰地景點<br />\n我推薦A+B線<br />\n<br />\n我自己都鐘意去埋小金門<br />\n都係坐十幾分鐘渡輪過去<br />\n然後小金門島上都有公車（南巡迴同埋北巡迴線）<br />\n幾多野可以影相<br />\n<br />\nSo-called台灣好行<br />\n其實即係我地ge巴士<br />\n但客運公司同旅遊局有協作<br />\n搞埋觀光線路方便遊客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要安裝好金門公車app<br />\n留意早幾分鐘去等車<br />\n金門公車係超方便同埋準時架"},{"pid":"d99c41be5930ef81daf1e8fa0336348181a14890","tid":147622,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"去過三日兩夜<br />\n其實可以玩多日<br />\n<br />\n不過個時租車時間好用啲，如果搭車你要預多啲時間"},{"pid":"c8ae7298ef02b6e97fa78a413795627058f9d47f","tid":147622,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"我都打算去WOR 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ae0a2600549faa1c00e0e6e628206dbe8ae90","tid":147622,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T22:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過三日兩夜<br />\n其實可以玩多日<br />\n<br />\n不過個時租車時間好用啲，如果搭車你要預多啲時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我同男友唔識揸車吖嘛"},{"pid":"050e5c00b354e8c9aa660fe35874d5d65ca0c344","tid":147622,"uid":66540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"金門正啊 前年去過一次 好推薦<br />\n可以既話建議留3-4日 係一個好悠閒既地方<br />\n用2日搭台灣好行 A B C D 線 可以去晒<br />\n搵半日過小金門行下都唔錯 仲有太武山<br />\n如果無車 想方便既話最好住金城鎮<br />\n啲人好 nice 又熱情 又純樸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔似對岸污煙瘴氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d32cc9c5d3de65755ebd94d0d52bb7b011439a","tid":147622,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金門正啊 前年去過一次 好推薦<br />\n可以既話建議留3-4日 係一個好悠閒既地方<br />\n用2日搭台灣好行 A B C D 線 可以去晒<br />\n搵半日過小金門行下都唔錯 仲有太武山<br />\n如果無車 想方便既話最好住金城鎮<br />\n啲人好 nice 又熱情 又純樸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔似對岸污煙瘴氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次係廈門過金門, 兩邊個分別大到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc8aad9c5f7a9cee5477b48474d4d47a7ee8d61","tid":147622,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"係匪區過去啲船密唔密？"},{"pid":"2b38fcf73fbae8c2cbdb8f1cd7c815d77e801d8d","tid":147622,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"仲想問下係匪區撘膠鐵去啲飛點買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a048984539bcb728b4e83baa7462e55d6d88b29","tid":147622,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係匪區過去啲船密唔密？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔算密<br />\n所以最好上網預訂船飛<br />\n唔好諗住到時買<br />\n<br />\n淘寶幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}